Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门之海波涛汹涌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹与联邦两军的暗中活动各怀心机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中形成会合点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到敌作战计划书的巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获悉了卡多可怕的目地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在此时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他受损的机体化为星尘消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对失去能仰赖的人的宏·浦木来说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的军衔章太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后是宿命的阅舰式的当日…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}所罗门的恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,00)\fs40}阿克西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于联邦实行地球圈的主权掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止其实现的唯一手段就是迪拉兹的起义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与他们分道扬镳已有三年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看来彼此的志向仍然一致
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们反攻的力量终究还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先遣舰队到何处了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照预定航线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正向与迪拉兹舰队的会合点前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，搭载MA的调整也没有延误
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大义…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要在这里待多少年？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0040,,{\fad(150,00)\fs35}阿克西斯先遣舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹阁下来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢对大义的赞同及“星尘”的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽有些微的时间差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已能直接通信了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是他的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加电信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位同志，欢迎来地球圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一样擅于感人落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0300,,{\fad(150,200)\fs40}金米岛·限制海域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手向金米岛方面逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压制住他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我干这个也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我会处理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击落三架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是正规军却接二连三的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想参加迪拉兹舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想与卡多会合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这所罗门之海的某处…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fad(150,340)\fs45}暗礁宙域·金米岛中间点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星尘作战也进入最终阶段了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣的各舰队也照预定行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是一切的终结吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投下我们全战力的这个作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将遭受相当大的损失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无力再射出第二支箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就会坠落了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解您的心情，阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在万一的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:06:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我即使中止作战也必须撤兵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像屈辱的阿·巴瓦·库一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0040,,{\fad(150,240)\fs38}所罗门海域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷却垫圈好了，要把管道接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的，打开回路，快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了要检查一下10号马达吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把备用钻头拿过来！1-3的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，良好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，能调换吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不适吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起在这片大海中阵亡的同胞就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾直接跟随少佐战斗的人就只剩我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到众多英灵漂流的此地来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我岂非立于众多的牺牲之上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是指挥者的宿命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片海还太年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要风平浪静下来还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是奔驰而过罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这一刻，大家齐集合于此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走了吗？军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击前20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请上到MS甲板去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝特大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-1-0有一不明机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航道清除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连吃饭的时间也没有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德尔机的补给延误了2分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我自己掏钱做鸭子料理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的敌机是第几架？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到第11架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于浦木中尉与吉斯少尉的归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉拉贝拉管制区防卫减弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们加快补给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距阅舰式还剩1小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主力舰艇几乎都在金米岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让地球如此空虚真的行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长到现在还认为GUNDAM2号机的目标是贾布罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只怕万一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过幕僚会议想以阅舰式为饵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气做了断，未免太心急了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德尔机GM Cannon要起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊，击落3架…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片海是地狱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚部进行总线走向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做一次与定位器的同步检测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯少尉没打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部位强制开放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已出击3次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，现在有点汗臭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没察觉这里的气味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密闭的军舰气味还真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐气和体臭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还渗杂着机油味…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知是怎么了，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？舒服点了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是俘虏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如所见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想好好听他说说迪拉兹舰队的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了，蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说我违反条约吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该明白现在不是讲大道理的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有大志的你们终究会灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让所罗门的恶梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重现的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0080,,{\fad(200,140)\fs42}地球联邦军·金米岛·镇守府
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这金米岛如此安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪还有ZION军在徘徊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的警戒网是万全的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止已击毁37架敌MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢来的话就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此散漫的攻击还想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪会有人想通敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候去旗舰伯明翰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绅士必须要准时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次阅舰式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向太空住民们展现联邦实力的绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪式的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味着迪拉兹舰队的败北吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS要射出了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人员请回避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了，祝武运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀旧的宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击的信号弹怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但、但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本作战的成否可说是取决于奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事就让敌人识破的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上天终究是不站在我们这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只有前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯特尔巡哨区有新的敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏、浦木、吉斯各机请与贝特机会合，加以迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗要持续到何时？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我逮到卡多为止吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航道清除，祝好运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙历0079年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是上次的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人类而言是最坏的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡过这个困难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在事隔三年后又能举行宇宙一大盛典的阅舰式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为将地球圈的安定与和平具体化之一员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人喜不自胜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来，阅舰式是在地球历1341年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英法战争之际
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由英国的爱德华三世亲自观阅出击舰队而肇始的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应当共享的大宇宙之恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若任由部份卑劣之徒蹂躏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂能容许联邦说出那种鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急着赴死，现在要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手握活着才能得到的那份荣光为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命就托付于我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对逝去的英灵的亵渎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在都已经在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了扫除联邦的贪婪之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗盘上没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那演说特地为我们引路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冲入湾内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了护卫机以外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都照预定进行诱敌扰乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十、十手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}十手：一种可隔架刀剑的钝器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这区域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主队在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多虽说只有一机，但持有核弹头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mk.82吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那疑似信号弹的报告呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人还会特地鸣枪起跑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-3及L-7正在迎击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹的目标一定是这仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹的舰队才会葬身海底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去教教他们没有MS的舰队会有何下场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受阅舰艇第3群由左舷通过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是警备卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是警备卫星4号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Orange3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭敌机枪攻击，请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉摩斯巡哨区大量敌MS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在请求增援
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是“主宾”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让附近的MS去“欢迎”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝特大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝特大尉听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉摩斯巡哨区确认到疑似敌主力部队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请急速赶去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G区77
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻前往该地点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸭子料理煮得如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2号机…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到卡多了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前没有情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前还没有情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有这么多所罗门之战的残骸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此联邦的家伙们也难以察知我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片海在哭泣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对我们诉说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在欢迎我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能听得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木！背后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是高手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:21:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于之前的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是卡多再来这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行退避行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里不知瞒过联邦的耳目出击过多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此“星尘”就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动炮台？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发觉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还有新的敌机？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-0暗礁空域2架
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影像传送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多在S-0？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里来得及赶去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Full Burnern的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我们，吉斯也去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再耽搁下去会误了大事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，这里交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去金米岛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！去所罗门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下 宏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.93,0:24:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独行动很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.16,0:24:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.08,0:24:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候已久的时刻到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了证明许多英灵并非平白丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的警戒算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.43,0:25:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2号机？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.27,0:25:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米岛的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.54,0:25:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为再次高揭ZION的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.80,0:25:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦为成就“星尘”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.04,0:25:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门啊！我回来了

Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.41,0:27:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预    告
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.13,0:28:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米岛溢出了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激震的宇宙哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.60,0:28:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐实现的迪拉兹的策谋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.95,0:28:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有无法洗刷的浦木的屈辱感
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM1号机对2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.82,0:28:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场宿命的最后之战开始时
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.68,0:28:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朦胧的“星尘”显现在浦木的眼前
